Patches-Solid-Colors

  extensions [import-a]

  to-report all-greens       report "data:image/png;base64," end
  to-report all-pinks        report "data:image/png;base64," end
  to-report all-hundreds-rgb report "data:image/png;base64," end

  O> resize-world -16 16 -16 16

  O> import-a:pcolors all-greens
  count patches with [pcolor = green] => 1089

  O> import-a:pcolors-rgb all-greens
  count patches with [pcolor = (extract-rgb green)] => 1089

  O> import-a:pcolors all-pinks
  count patches with [pcolor = pink] => 1089

  O> import-a:pcolors-rgb all-pinks
  count patches with [pcolor = (extract-rgb pink)] => 1089

  O> import-a:pcolors all-hundreds-rgb
  count patches with [pcolor = (approximate-rgb 100 100 100)] => 1089

  O> import-a:pcolors-rgb all-hundreds-rgb
  count patches with [pcolor = [100 100 100]] => 1089

Patches-All-But-One

  extensions [import-a]

  to-report all-but-one-black report "data:image/png;base64," end

  O> resize-world -16 16 -16 16

  O> import-a:pcolors all-but-one-black
  count patches with [pcolor = black] => 1088
  [pcolor] of patch 0 0 => 115

  O> import-a:pcolors-rgb all-but-one-black
  count patches with [pcolor = (extract-rgb black)] => 1088
  [pcolor] of patch 0 0 => [124 80 164]

Patches-All-But-One-JPEG

  extensions [import-a]
